<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="23Mar1933"><font color="red">23 March 1933</font> <i>Letters III</i> (to Harriet Weaver from Paul L&eacute;on): All these bad thoughts are due in a small degree to the fact that he is yet unable to concentrate his mind on his work &hellip; For I do think Mr Joyce belongs to his work and unless he is able to do it he will not get well </div>
